			<view isee:template_view="template:3" isee:name="Intro" background="white" page_width="1066" page_height="600" zoom="165" home_view="true" type="interface">
				<style>
					<isee:stacked_container item_spacing="0" corner_radius="4" selected_item_color="black" selected_item_background="white" item_background="#DDDDDD" transparent_bg="false"/>
				</style>
				<button background="#587FC1" font_weight="bold" font_color="white" border_width="thin" border_style="none" corner_radius="5" isee:flat="true" label="Go to Simulator" isee:tooltip="" x="915.272" y="172.108" width="135" height="30">
					<actions>
						<action target="interface:2">navigate</action>
					</actions>
				</button>
				<button background="#587FC1" font_weight="bold" font_color="white" border_width="thin" border_style="none" corner_radius="5" isee:flat="true" label="Go to Storyboard" isee:tooltip="" x="915.272" y="122.174" width="135" height="30">
					<actions>
						<action target="story" view="0" story="120">navigate</action>
					</actions>
				</button>
				<text_box font_family="segoe ui" x="678.11" y="114.042" width="225" height="54.2642">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;The storyboard gives a high-level overview of the model and its structure, and explains the logic behind the model. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text_box>
				<text_box font_family="segoe ui" x="677.472" y="174.739" width="216.667" height="24.7373">Go to the simulator to explore
</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="710.959" y="499.615" width="243.795" height="55">Use these buttons to run the model in steps or all the way to the end. You can change settings between steps and then run the model for a period to see the impact.</text_box>
				<text_box z_index="6" background="#2C2825" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="12.815" y="499.615" width="209.989" height="55">Grey buttons are reset buttons:
&apos;Clear Graphs&apos; - clears the charts shown
&apos;Reset Inputs&apos; -  restores all inputs to their defaults.</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" text_align="center" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="378.01" y="499.615" width="213.244" height="55">Use these buttons to run the model to the end. You can pause along the way and adjust values. </text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" text_align="center" vertical_text_align="center" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="230.433" y="499.615" width="142.633" height="55">&apos;Run live&apos; allows you to see changes made to inputs immediately, across the whole simulation period.</text_box>
				<graphics_frame fill="none" x="838.723" y="407.566" width="35" height="30">
					<image width="36" height="39" size_to_parent="true" isee:transparency="0" isee:fixed_aspect_ratio="true">data:image/png;base64,</image>
				</graphics_frame>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="872.723" y="419.089" width="175" height="33.5227">Reset an individual input to its default value</text_box>
				<text_box background="#2C2825" font_color="white" font_family="segoe ui" font_size="9pt" padding="5" x="873.609" y="366.216" width="175" height="34.9459">Hover over the Info button for more detail on how to use the feature</text_box>
				<isee:annotation transparent="true" isee:flat="true" popup_background_color="white" launcher_label="" show_by_default="false" hide_launcher="false" launch_on_hover="true" x="843.723" y="361.333" width="25" height="25">
					<launcher_image width="96" height="96" size_to_parent="true">data:image/png;base64,</launcher_image>
					<popup hide_when_editing="true" x="623.5" y="363.813" width="203" height="117.506">
						<text>A pop-up with more information will appear when you hover over the Info button.

Click outside the pop-up to return to the main screen.</text>
					</popup>
				</isee:annotation>
				<text_box x="23.148" y="78.4" width="557.203" height="414.8">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Introduction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Good perioperative care leads to improved outcomes for both patients and the system, such as reduced avoidable complications, earlier patient discharge from hospital after surgery, and more efficient use of resources which releases capacity. Within the NHS, the perioperative care pathway is a complex, interconnected system, spanning multiple disciplines and organisations. Modelling the whole pathway can improve the understanding of how changes in one part of the system can have ripple effects across the entire system. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;This simulator models the whole pathway, with a specific focus on elective hip and knee surgical pathways. The tool has been developed for a range of healthcare staff, including health service planners and commissioners. It brings together a range of evidence-based information, along with practice and expert-informed insights, to illustrate the benefits of early screening and other interventions (including health improvement activities). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;These benefits can be realised in both service efficiencies, and also through improved patient and population outcomes. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;This tool has been developed with NHS medical, nursing, public health and service commissioning experts and includes input from the Centre for Perioperative Care, the Royal College of Anaesthetists, the Royal College of Surgeons, GIRFT and leads from Integrated Care Boards. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;This resource is built using a system dynamics methodology and data-informed modelling assumptions, and aims to provide an evidence and practice-base informed high-level model to help support service planners, commissioners and decision-makers. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text_box>
			</view>
			<view isee:template_view="template:2" isee:name="Validation" background="white" page_width="1066" page_height="600" zoom="125" type="interface">
				<style>
					<isee:stacked_container item_spacing="0" corner_radius="4" selected_item_color="black" selected_item_background="white" item_background="#DDDDDD" transparent_bg="false"/>
				</style>
				<stacked_container x="277.071" y="111.077" width="245" height="200">
					<graph font_size="10pt" isee:hide_border="true" axis_title_font_size="10pt" width="245" height="200" type="time_series" show_grid="false" isee:tick_type="none" include_units_in_legend="false" plot_numbers="false" isee:label_pie_slices="false" isee:show_pie_borders="true" num_x_grid_lines="0" num_y_grid_lines="0" num_x_labels="5" num_y_labels="3" isee:fill_intensity="0.1" to="366" isee:allow_zero_axis="true" left_axis_multi_scale="false" left_axis_auto_scale="true" left_include_units="true" right_axis_multi_scale="false" right_axis_auto_scale="true" right_include_units="true">
						<plot color="#5881C1" title="WLMDS: open pathways" isee:keep_zero_visible="true" pen_width="2" index="0" show_y_axis="true">
							<entity name='calcs."der_rtt_h&amp;k"'/>
						</plot>
						<plot color="#EC6555" title="Total open pathways" isee:keep_zero_visible="true" pen_width="2" index="1" show_y_axis="true">
							<entity name="total_in_pathway"/>
						</plot>
					</graph>
				</stacked_container>
