				<text_box x="58.4615" y="356.923" width="162.48" height="22.6154">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Arial&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;FLOWS PER MONTH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text_box>
				<text_box x="279.231" y="78.4615" width="105.68" height="22.6154">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Arial&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:700; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;STOCKS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text_box>
				<text_box font_family="segoe ui" font_size="11pt" x="14.1447" y="82.6105" width="243.8" height="263.087">Model (red) is validated against known data (blue), using 2025 published RTT data, Waiting List Minimum Dataset (WLMDS) clock starts and clock stops.

Assumptions are required as it is not possible to identify referrals related to Hips &amp; Knees from other O&amp;T referrals.

 - Calibration optimisation is used to determine the proportion of all O&amp;T referrals that are for Hips &amp; Knees (~19%)

 - Hip &amp; Knee replacements are ~28% of all O&amp;T pathways with a Decision To Admit


</text_box>
