				<text_box uid="47" x="28.75" y="110" width="272" height="169">Uses referral rates for ALL ortho &amp; trauma referrals,
then applies conversion for hips and knees.

Model starts in 2025 (using 18+ 2025 populations for England)

Average growth rate is average of annual growth from 2025 to 2035</text_box>
				<aux background="#F9BF07" x="719.75" y="174" name="referrals per day"/>
